snippet.title: For Honor – Viking Gameplay Walkthrough Trailer - E3 2016
snippet.description:
Find out more about the Campaign mode : http://ubi.li/c76z9
Sign up for the alpha : http://ubi.li/nq7q4

Become the brutal Viking, the bold Knight or the deadly Samurai and rush into the chaos of the battlefield with this E3 demo.

Coming out 14th February 2017 on PS4, Xbox One and PC
